            77 => 
            array (
                'id' => 80,
                'product_id' => 1,
                'question' => '{"en":"How do zeolites work?","pl":"Jak dzia\\u0142aj\\u0105 zeolity?","jp":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u304c\\u3069\\u3093\\u306a\\u52b9\\u679c\\u3092\\u3082\\u305f\\u3089\\u3059\\u306e\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","ja":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u304c\\u3069\\u3093\\u306a\\u52b9\\u679c\\u3092\\u3082\\u305f\\u3089\\u3059\\u306e\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"How do zeolites work?","th":"How do zeolites work?"}',
            'answer' => '{"en":"<p>The porous nature of the zeolite &ldquo;cage&rdquo; and its negative charge, allows for the selective exchange of positively-charged toxins. Inside each zeolite are positively-charged exchangeable (lighter) metals known as cations, usually calcium, magnesium, sodium and potassium.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>These ions are only loosely held and can be readily displaced by other substances, such as toxic heavy metals or other organics in a process called cationic exchange. Zeolites have a preference or affinity for heavy metals due to the positive charge and fit of heavy metals within the zeolite cage.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Porowaty charakter \\"klatki\\" zeolitowej i jej \\u0142adunku ujemnego pozwala na selektywn\\u0105 wymian\\u0119 dodatnio na\\u0142adowanych toksyn. Wewn\\u0105trz ka\\u017cdego zeolitu znajduj\\u0105 si\\u0119 dodatnio na\\u0142adowane, wymienne (l\\u017cejsze) metale znane jako kationy, zwykle wap\\u0144, magnez, s&oacute;d i potas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Jony te s\\u0105 tylko lu\\u017ano trzymane i mog\\u0105 by\\u0107 \\u0142atwo przemieszczone przez inne substancje, takie jak toksyczne metale ci\\u0119\\u017ckie lub inne substancje organiczne w procesie zwanym wymian\\u0105 kationow\\u0105. Zeolity maj\\u0105 preferencje lub powinowactwo do metali ci\\u0119\\u017ckich ze wzgl\\u0119du na dodatni \\u0142adunek i dopasowanie metali ci\\u0119\\u017ckich w klatce zeolitowej.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306e\\u591a\\u5b54\\u6027\\u304a\\u3088\\u3073\\u305d\\u306e\\u8ca0\\u96fb\\u8377\\u3068\\u3044\\u3046\\u7279\\u6027\\u306f\\u3001\\u6b63\\u96fb\\u8377\\u306e\\u6bd2\\u7d20\\u306e\\u9078\\u629e\\u7684\\u4ea4\\u63db\\u3092\\u53ef\\u80fd\\u306b\\u3057\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002\\u5404\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306e\\u5185\\u90e8\\u306b\\u306f\\u3001\\u967d\\u30a4\\u30aa\\u30f3\\u3068\\u3057\\u3066\\u77e5\\u3089\\u308c\\u308b\\u6b63\\u96fb\\u8377\\u306e\\u4ea4\\u63db\\u53ef\\u80fd\\u306a\\uff08\\u3088\\u308a\\u8e