te is absorbed through the small intestine (villi). Most other zeolite supplements have a minimal percentage of sub-micron particles, so the majority goes to the large intestine for a limited detox effect.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pure Body undergoes a proprietary process to create a particle size of 0.4 microns (mean average) so the majority of particles are smaller than 0.2 microns for absorption via the small intestine, while the remainder proceeds to the colon.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Why so small? Zeolites do not dissolve in water; hence they cannot use water as the absorption mechanism used by many foods and medications, and must rely on size alone to get into the bloodstream.<\\/p>","th":"<p>When properly sized, zeolite is absorbed through the small intestine (villi). Most other zeolite supplements have a minimal percentage of sub-micron particles, so the majority goes to the large intestine for a limited detox effect.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pure Body undergoes a proprietary process to create a particle size of 0.4 microns (mean average) so the majority of particles are smaller than 0.2 microns for absorption via the small intestine, while the remainder proceeds to the colon.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Why so small? Zeolites do not dissolve in water; hence they cannot use water as the absorption mechanism used by many foods and medications, and must rely on size alone to get into the bloodstream.<\\/p>"}',
