            89 => 
            array (
                'id' => 92,
                'product_id' => 1,
                'question' => '{"en":"If zeolite is formed from silicon and aluminum, can aluminum be released into the body?","pl":"Je\\u015bli zeolit tworzy si\\u0119 z krzemu i aluminium, czy aluminium mo\\u017ce by\\u0107 uwalniane do organizmu?","jp":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u304c\\u30b7\\u30ea\\u30b3\\u30f3\\u3084\\u30a2\\u30eb\\u30df\\u30cb\\u30a6\\u30e0\\u304b\\u3089\\u4f5c\\u3089\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u3042\\u308c\\u3070\\u3001\\u30a2\\u30eb\\u30df\\u30cb\\u30a6\\u30e0\\u304c\\u4f53\\u5185\\u306b\\u653e\\u51fa\\u3055\\u308c\\u3066\\u3057\\u307e\\u3046\\u3053\\u3068\\u304c\\u3042\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u306f\\u306a\\u3044\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","ja":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u304c\\u30b7\\u30ea\\u30b3\\u30f3\\u3084\\u30a2\\u30eb\\u30df\\u30cb\\u30a6\\u30e0\\u304b\\u3089\\u4f5c\\u3089\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u3042\\u308c\\u3070\\u3001\\u30a2\\u30eb\\u30df\\u30cb\\u30a6\\u30e0\\u304c\\u4f53\\u5185\\u306b\\u653e\\u51fa\\u3055\\u308c\\u3066\\u3057\\u307e\\u3046\\u3053\\u3068\\u304c\\u3042\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u306f\\u306a\\u3044\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"If zeolite is formed from silicon and aluminum, can aluminum be released into the body?","th":"If zeolite is formed from silicon and aluminum, can aluminum be released into the body?"}',
                'answer' => '{"en":"<p>No. There is no &ldquo;free&rdquo; aluminum in the zeolite; it is part of the molecular structure of the zeolite. This form of aluminum is totally inert and does not interact with the body in any way, as proven in numerous studies.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This is further demonstrated in our third-party tested chemical analysis, where the zeolite cage was dissolved using a strong acid mixture called Aqua Regia, and shows the chemical constituent of aluminum.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The molecular structure of zeolite is indestructible in the body. Zeolites are neither water nor fat soluble, and the molecule can withstand high heat.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Nie. W zeolicie nie ma \\"wolnego\\" aluminium; jest cz\\u0119\\u015bci\\u0105 struktury molekularnej zeolitu. Ta forma aluminium jest ca\\u0142kowicie oboj\\u0119tna i w \\u017caden spos&oacute;b nie wsp&oacute;\\u0142dzia\\u0142a z cia\\u0142em, co potwierdzaj\\u0105 liczne badania.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Zosta\\u0142o to dodatkowo wykazane w naszej analizie chemicznej przeprowadzonej przez niezale\\u017cn\\u0105 firm\\u0119, w kt&oacute;rej klatk\\u0119 zeolitow\\u0105 rozpuszczono stosuj\\u0105c mocn\\u0105 mieszanin\\u0119 kwas&oacute;w o nazwie Aqua Regia i kt&oacute;ra pokazuje sk\\u0142adnik chemiczny aluminium.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Struktura molekularna zeolitu jest niezniszczalna w ciele. Zeolity nie s\\u0105 ani rozpuszczalne w wodzie, ani w t\\u0142uszczu, a cz\\u0105steczka mo\\u017ce wytrzyma\\u0107 wysokie temperatury.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>\\u3044\\u3044\\u3048\\u3002\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306e\\u4e2d\\u306b\\u306f\\u3001\\u5358\\u72ec\\u3067\\u5b58\\u5728\\u3059\\u308b\\u30a2\\u30eb\\u30df\\u30cb\\u30a6\\u30e0\\u306f\\u3042\\u308a\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093\\u3002\\u3064\\u307e\\u308a\\u3001\\u3053\\u3053\\u306b\\u3042\\u308b\\u30a2\\u30eb\\u30df\\u30cb\\u30a6\\u30e0\\u306f\\u3001\\u3059\\u3067\\u306b\\u3001\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u5206\\u5b50\\u69cb\\u9020\\u306e\\u4e00\\u90e8\\u306