                'question' => '{"en":"Why is a liquid better than a powdered zeolite?","pl":"Dlaczego ciecz jest lepsza ni\\u017c sproszkowany zeolit?","jp":"\\u306a\\u305c\\u30ea\\u30ad\\u30c3\\u30c9\\u30bf\\u30a4\\u30d7\\u306f\\u7c89\\u672b\\u72b6\\u3088\\u308a\\u3082\\u512a\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","ja":"\\u306a\\u305c\\u30ea\\u30ad\\u30c3\\u30c9\\u30bf\\u30a4\\u30d7\\u306f\\u7c89\\u672b\\u72b6\\u3088\\u308a\\u3082\\u512a\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"Why is a liquid better than a powdered zeolite?","th":"Why is a liquid better than a powdered zeolite?"}',
            'answer' => '{"en":"<p>In addition to knowing the composition and cleanliness of the zeolite, particle size is paramount in determining the absorption of the zeolite in the body. Most powdered zeolites are large in particle size making it ineffective for systemic detoxification and unpleasant to drink scoops of powder in water.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Individual sub-micron particles (less than one millionth of a meter) are not visible to the naked eye. The percentage of sub-micron particles in a powdered zeolite can be easily lost in the air moving it from the canister to the water.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The proven particle size of Pure Body ensures optimal detoxification and trillions of tiny particles are suspended in water so you get the benefit of each one.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Opr&oacute;cz znajomo\\u015bci sk\\u0142adu i czysto\\u015bci zeolitu, wielko\\u015b\\u0107 cz\\u0105stek jest najwa\\u017cniejsza przy okre\\u015blaniu wch\\u0142aniania zeolitu w organizmie. Wi\\u0119kszo\\u015b\\u0107 sproszkowanych zeolit&oacute;w ma du\\u017cy rozmiar cz\\u0105stek, co sprawia, \\u017ce s\\u0105 nieskuteczne w przypadku systemowej detoksykacji i nieprzyjemne w piciu miarki proszku w wodzie.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pojedyncze cz\\u0105stki submikronowe (mniej ni\\u017c jedna milionowa metra) nie s\\u0105 widoczne go\\u0142ym okiem. Procent cz\\u0105stek submikronowych w sproszkowanym zeolicie mo\\u017cna \\u0142atwo utraci\\u0107 w powietrzu, przenosz\\u0105c go z pojemnika do wody.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sprawdzony rozmiar cz\\u0105steczek Pure Body zapewnia optymaln\\u0105 detoksykacj\\u0119, a tryliony drobnych cz\\u0105steczek s\\u0105 zawieszone w wodzie, dzi\\u0119ki czemu zyskujesz korzy\\u015bci ka\\u017cdego z nich.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306e\\u7d44\\u6210\\u304a\\u3088\\u3073\\u6e05\\u6d44\\u306e\\u5ea6\\u5408\\u3044\\u3092\\u77e5\\u308b\\u3053\\u3068\\u306b\\u52a0\\u3048\\u3066\\u3001\\u7c92\\u5b50\\u30b5\\u30a4\\u30ba\\u306f\\u3001\\u4f53\\u5185\\u3067\\