                'question' => '{"en":"Why should I avoid zeolites supplements with vitamins and minerals?","pl":"Dlaczego powinienem unika\\u0107 suplement\\u00f3w zeolitowych z witaminami i minera\\u0142ami?","jp":"\\u30d3\\u30bf\\u30df\\u30f3\\u3084\\u30df\\u30cd\\u30e9\\u30eb\\u306e\\u5165\\u3063\\u305f\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u30b5\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30e1\\u30f3\\u30c8\\u3092\\u907f\\u3051\\u308b\\u3079\\u304d\\u7406\\u7531\\u3068\\u306f\\uff1f","ja":"\\u30d3\\u30bf\\u30df\\u30f3\\u3084\\u30df\\u30cd\\u30e9\\u30eb\\u306e\\u5165\\u3063\\u305f\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u30b5\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30e1\\u30f3\\u30c8\\u3092\\u907f\\u3051\\u308b\\u3079\\u304d\\u7406\\u7531\\u3068\\u306f\\uff1f","es":"Why should I avoid zeolites supplements with vitamins and minerals?","th":"Why should I avoid zeolites supplements with vitamins and minerals?"}',
                'answer' => '{"en":"<p>To create an effective zeolite supplement, the zeolite cages of Pure Body are filled with exchangeable cations of calcium, magnesium, sodium and potassium. The zeolite particles are then placed in pure water for a liquid zeolite suspension, ready to detox your body.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>There are other zeolite providers who mix zeolites in a liquid base of synthetic vitamins, or other substances. Synthetic vitamins can carry a positive charge. And while zeolites have an affinity for highly-charged toxins, sitting the zeolite cages for months with substances that carry even a weak positive charge could lead the zeolite to absorb those materials, and render it ineffective for detoxing the body.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Aby stworzy\\u0107 skuteczny suplement zeolitu, klatki zeolitowe Pure Body s\\u0105 wype\\u0142nione wymiennymi kationami wapnia, magnezu, sodu i potasu. Cz\\u0105stki zeolitu s\\u0105 nast\\u0119pnie umieszczane w czystej wodzie dla ciek\\u0142ej zawiesiny zeolitu, gotowej do detoksykacji cia\\u0142a.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>S\\u0105 inni dostawcy zeolit&oacute;w, kt&oacute;rzy mieszaj\\u0105 zeolity w p\\u0142ynnej bazie syntetycznych witamin lub innych substancji. Syntetyczne witaminy mog\\u0105 mie\\u0107 \\u0142adunek dodatni. Podczas gdy zeolity maj\\u0105 powinowactwo do silnie na\\u0142adowanych toksyn, odk\\u0142adanie klatek zeolitu na miesi\\u0105ce substancjami, kt&oacute;re nios\\u0105 nawet s\\u0142aby \\u0142adunek dodatni, mo\\u017ce doprowadzi\\u0107 zeolit do wch\\u0142oni\\u0119cia tych materia\\u0142&oacute;w i uczyni\\u0107 go nieskutecznym do detoksykacji cia\\u0142a.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>\\u52b9\\u679c\\u7684\\u306a\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u30b5\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30e1\\u30f3\\u30c8\\u4f5c\\u88fd\\u306e\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u3001\\u30d4\\u30e5\\u30a2\\u30dc\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u306b\\u4f7f\\u7528\\u3055\\u308c\\u308b\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8&ldquo;\\u30b1\\u30fc\\u30b8&rdquo;\\u306f\\u3001\\u4ea4\\u63db\\u53