                'question' => '{"en":"Are there any side effects in taking zeolite?","pl":"Czy s\\u0105 jakie\\u015b efekty uboczne przy przyjmowaniu zeolitu?","jp":"Are there any side effects in taking zeolite?","ja":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306e\\u6442\\u53d6\\u306b\\u306f\\u4f55\\u304b\\u526f\\u4f5c\\u7528\\u304c\\u3042\\u308a\\u307e\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"Are there any side effects in taking zeolite?","th":"Are there any side effects in taking zeolite?"}',
            'answer' => '{"en":"<p>The zeolite Clinoptilolite has been granted GRAS (Generally Recognized As Safe) status by the Food and Drug Administration. Since zeolites will attract water to facilitate the detoxification process, adequate filtered water intake is suggested (8 to 10 glasses a day). If any signs of dehydration do appear (headaches, tiredness), increase your water intake and reduce your zeolite intake for that day.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Zeolit Clinoptilolite uzyska\\u0142 status GRAS (og&oacute;lnie uwa\\u017cane za bezpieczny) przez Food and Drug Administration. Poniewa\\u017c zeolity przyci\\u0105gaj\\u0105 wod\\u0119 w celu u\\u0142atwienia procesu detoksyfikacji, sugeruje si\\u0119 odpowiedni\\u0105 ilo\\u015b\\u0107 przefiltrowanej wody (od 8 do 10 szklanek dziennie). Je\\u015bli pojawi\\u0105 si\\u0119 oznaki odwodnienia (b&oacute;le g\\u0142owy, zm\\u0119czenie), zwi\\u0119ksz spo\\u017cycie wody i zmniejsz spo\\u017cycie zeolitu na ten dzie\\u0144.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>The zeolite Clinoptilolite has been granted GRAS (Generally Recognized As Safe) status by the Food and Drug Administration. Since zeolites will attract water to facilitate the detoxification process, adequate filtered water intake is suggested (8 to 10 glasses a day). If any signs of dehydration do appear (headaches, tiredness), increase your water intake and reduce your zeolite intake for that day.<\\/p>","ja":"<p>\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u30af\\u30ea\\u30ce\\u30d7\\u30c1\\u30ed\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306b\\u306f\\u3001FDA\\u3088\\u308aGRAS\\uff08\\u4e00\\u822c\\u306b\\u5b89\\u5168\\u3068\\u8a8d\\u3081\\u3089\\u308c\\u308b\\uff09\\u3068\\u3044\\u3046\\u8a55\\u4fa1\\u304c\\u4e0b\\u3055\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u3001\\u30c7\\u30c8\\u30c3\\u30af\\u30b9\\u4f5c\\u696d\\u306e\\u4fc3\\u9032\\u306e\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u6c34\\u3092\\u4f7f\\u7528\\u3059\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u3001\\u5341\\u5206\\u306a\\u91cf\\u306e\\u6e05\\u6f54\\u306a\\u6c34\\u306e\\u6442\\u53d6\\uff081\\u65e5\\u30b3\\u30c3\\u30d78\\u301c9\\u676f\\u306e\\u6c34\\uff09\\u304c\\u63a8\\u5968\\u3055\\u308c\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002\\u6c34\\u5206\\u4e0d\\u8db3\\u306e\\u5146\\u5019\\u304c\\u3001\\u4e07\\u304c\\u4e00\\u898b\\u3089\\u308c\\u305f\\u5834\\u5408\\uff08\\u982d\\u75db\\u3001\\u75b2\\u52b4\\u611f\\u306a\\u3069\\uff09\\u306b\\u306f\\u3001\\u305d\\u306e\\u65e5\\u306e\\u3001\\u6c34\\u5206\\u6442\\u53d6\\u91cf\\u3092\\u5897\\u3084\\u3057\\u3001\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u6442\\u53d6\\u91cf\\u3092\\u6e1b\\u3089\\u3059\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u3057\\u3066\\u304f\\u3060\\u3055\\u3044\\u3002<\\/p>","es":"<p>The zeolite Clinoptilolite has been granted GRAS (Generally Recognized As Safe) status by the Food and Drug Administration. Since zeolites will attract water to facilitate the detoxification process, adequate filtered water intake is suggested (8 to 10 glasses a day). If any signs of dehydration do appear (headaches, tiredness), increase your water intake and reduce your zeolite intake for that day.<\\/p>","th":"<p>The zeolite Clinoptilolite has been granted GRAS (Generally Recognized As Safe) status by the Food and Drug Administration. Since zeolites will attract water to facilitate the detoxification process, adequate filtered water intake is suggested (8 to 10 glasses a day). If any signs of dehydration do appear (headaches, tiredness), increase your water intake and reduce your zeolite intake for that day.<\\/p>"}',
