                'question' => '{"en":"How is zeolite absorbed into the body?","pl":"W jaki spos\\u00f3b zeolit jest wch\\u0142aniany przez organizm?","jp":"How is zeolite absorbed into the body?","ja":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u3069\\u306e\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u3057\\u3066\\u4f53\\u306b\\u5438\\u53ce\\u3055\\u308c\\u308b\\u306e\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"How is zeolite absorbed into the body?","th":"How is zeolite absorbed into the body?"}',
            'answer' => '{"en":"<p>When properly sized, zeolite is absorbed through the small intestine (villi). Most other zeolite supplements have a minimal percentage of sub-micron particles, so the majority goes to the large intestine for a limited detox effect.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pure Body Extra undergoes a proprietary process to create a particle size in the nanometer range so that it is fully absorbed into the bloodstream and travels with water throughout the body.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Przy w\\u0142a\\u015bciwym rozmiarze zeolit przenika przez jelito cienkie (kosmki). Wi\\u0119kszo\\u015b\\u0107 innych suplement&oacute;w zeolitowych ma minimalny udzia\\u0142 procentowy cz\\u0105stek submikronowych, wi\\u0119c wi\\u0119kszo\\u015b\\u0107 trafia do jelita grubego w celu uzyskania ograniczonego efektu detoksykacji.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pure Body Extra podlega autorskiemu procesowi tworzenia wielko\\u015bci cz\\u0105stek w zakresie nanometr&oacute;w, dzi\\u0119ki czemu jest w pe\\u0142ni wch\\u0142aniany do krwioobiegu i podr&oacute;\\u017cuje z wod\\u0105 w ca\\u0142ym ciele.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>When properly sized, zeolite is absorbed through the small intestine (villi). Most other zeolite supplements have a minimal percentage of sub-micron particles, so the majority goes to the large intestine for a limited detox effect.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Pure Body Extra Strength undergoes a proprietary process to create a particle size in the nanometer range so that it is fully absorbed into the bloodstream and travels with water throughout the body.<\\/p>","ja":"<p>\\u9069\\u5207\\u306a\\u30b5\\u30a4\\u30ba\\u306b\\u8abf\\u6574\\u3055\\u308c\\u305f\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u3001\\u5c0f\\u8178\\u304b\\u3089\\u4f53\\u5185\\u306b\\u5438\\u53ce\\u3055\\u308c\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002\\u4ed6\\u306e\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u30b5\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30e1\\u30f3\\u30c8\\u306e\\u7c92\\u306f\\u30b5\\u30d6\\u30df\\u30af\\u30ed\\u30f3\\u3067\\u3042\\u308a\\u3001\\u5927\\u90e8\\u5206\\u306f\