                'question' => '{"en":"Do zeolites remove good minerals in addition to the bad heavy metals?","pl":"Czy zeolity usun\\u0105\\u0107 dobrych minera\\u0142y, jak r\\u00f3wnie\\u017c z\\u0142e metale ci\\u0119\\u017ckie?","jp":"Do zeolites remove good minerals in addition to the bad heavy metals?","ja":"\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u6709\\u6bd2\\u306a\\u91cd\\u91d1\\u5c5e\\u3068\\u540c\\u6642\\u306b\\u597d\\u307e\\u3057\\u3044\\u30df\\u30cd\\u30e9\\u30eb\\u3082\\u9664\\u53bb\\u3057\\u3066\\u3057\\u307e\\u3044\\u307e\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"Do zeolites remove good minerals in addition to the bad heavy metals?","th":"Do zeolites remove good minerals in addition to the bad heavy metals?"}',
            'answer' => '{"en":"<p>No, zeolites only have an affinity for heavy metals and toxins. Clinoptilolite is a rare negatively-charged mineral. Most toxins and heavy metals are positively-charged. Like a magnet, the zeolite attracts and then traps positively-charged toxins before passing through the body.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>What makes zeolite so special is that it is highly selective and ONLY takes out toxins.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>During our proprietary cleansing process, the zeolite is filled with minerals such as calcium, magnesium and potassium. When it takes in a &ldquo;bad&rdquo; ion such as lead, it gives back a &ldquo;good&rdquo; ion such as calcium to the body. That means there is NO mineral depletion.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This swapping bad for good (or cation exchange) is what makes zeolite a highly effective and safe detox.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Nie, zeolity maj\\u0105 powinowactwo tylko do metali ci\\u0119\\u017ckich i toksyn. Klinoptylolit jest rzadkim, ujemnie na\\u0142adowanym minera\\u0142em. Wi\\u0119kszo\\u015b\\u0107 toksyn i metali ci\\u0119\\u017ckich jest na\\u0142adowanych dodatnio. Podobnie jak magnes, zeolit przyci\\u0105ga, a nast\\u0119pnie wychwytuje dodatnio na\\u0142adowane toksyny przed przej\\u015bciem przez cia\\u0142o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>To, co czyni zeolit tak wyj\\u0105tkowym, to to, \\u017ce jest wysoce selektywny i WY\\u0141\\u0104CZNIE usuwa toksyny.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Podczas naszego opatentowanego procesu oczyszczania, zeolit wype\\u0142nia si\\u0119 minera\\u0142ami takimi jak wap\\u0144, magnez i potas. Kiedy przyjmuje \\"z\\u0142y\\" jon, taki jak o\\u0142&oacute;w, oddaje do organizmu \\"dobry\\" jon, taki jak wap\\u0144. Oznacza to, \\u017ce nie ma wyczerpania minera\\u0142&oacute;w.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ta zamiana z\\u0142ej na dobr\\u0105 (lub wymiany kationowej) sprawia, \\u017ce zeolit jest wysoce skutecznym i bezpiecznym detoksykatorem.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>No, zeolites only have an affinity for heavy metals and toxins. Clinoptilolite is a rare negatively-charged mineral. Most toxins and heavy metals are positively-charged. Like a magnet, the zeolite attracts and then traps positively-charged toxins before passing through the body.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>What makes zeolite so special is that it is highly selective and ONLY takes out toxins.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>During our proprietary cleansing process, the zeolite is filled with minerals such as calcium, magnesium and potassium. When it takes in a &ldquo;bad&rdquo; ion such as lead, it gives back a &ldquo;good&rdquo; ion such as calcium to the body. That means there is NO mineral depletion.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This swapping bad for good (or cation exchange) is what makes zeolite a highly effective and safe detox.<\\/p>","ja":"<p>\\u3044\\u3044\\u3048\\u3001\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u91cd\\u91d1\\u5c5e\\u3084\\u6bd2\\u7d20\\u306b\\u3057\\u304b\\u89aa\\u548c\\u6027\\u304c\\u3042\\u308a\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093\\u3002 \\u30af\\u30ea\\u30ce\\u30d7\\u30c1\\u30ed\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u3001\\u7a00\\u5c11\\u306a\\u3001\\u8ca0\\u96fb\\u8377\\u306e\\u9271\\u7269\\u3067\\u3059\\u3002\\u307b\\u3068\\u3093\\u3069\\u306e\\u6bd2\\u7d20\\u3084\\u91cd\\u91d1\\u5c5e\\u306f\\u6b63\\u96fb\\u8377\\u3067\\u3042\\u308a\\u3001\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u78c1\\u77f3\\u306e\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u3001\\u4f53\\u5185\\u3092\\u901a\\u904e\\u3059\\u308b\\u969b\\u306b\\u3001\\u6b63\\u96fb\\u8377\\u306e\\u6bd2\\u7d20\\u3092\\u5f15\\u304d\\u4ed8\\u3051\\u88dc\\u8db3\\u3059\\u308b\\u7279\\u5fb4\\u3092\\u6301\\u3063\\u3066\\u3044\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306b\\u9855\\u8457\\u306a\\u70b9\\u3068\\u3057\\u3066\\u3001\\u3053\\u308c\\u306f\\u3001\\u975e\\u5e38\\u306b\\u9078\\u629e\\u7684\\u306b\\u6bd2\\u7d20\\u306e\\u307f\\u3092\\u6355\\u6349\\u3057\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u5f53\\u793e\\u72ec\\u81ea\\u306e\\u6d17\\u6d44\\u30d7\\u30ed\\u30bb\\u30b9\\u306b\\u3066\\u3001\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u30ab\\u30eb\\u30b