roduct, which shows what is bioavailable, shows NO available aluminum.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The molecular structure of zeolite is indestructible in the body. Zeolites are neither water nor fat soluble, and the molecule can withstand high heat.<\\/p>"}',
