                'question' => '{"en":"What special processing does Pure Body Extra Strength undergo?","pl":"Jakie specjalne przetwarzanie poddaje si\\u0119 dzia\\u0142aniu Pure Body Extra Strength?","jp":"\\u30d4\\u30e5\\u30a2\\u30dc\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30a8\\u30af\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30e9\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30ec\\u30f3\\u30b9\\u72ec\\u81ea\\u306e\\u7279\\u5225\\u306a\\u51e6\\u7406\\u65b9\\u6cd5\\u3068\\u306f\\u4f55\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","ja":"\\u30d4\\u30e5\\u30a2\\u30dc\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30a8\\u30af\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30e9\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30ec\\u30f3\\u30b9\\u72ec\\u81ea\\u306e\\u7279\\u5225\\u306a\\u51e6\\u7406\\u65b9\\u6cd5\\u3068\\u306f\\u4f55\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f","es":"What special processing does Pure Body Extra Strength undergo?","th":"What special processing does Pure Body Extra Strength undergo?"}',
            'answer' => '{"en":"<p>We properly size the zeolite for maximum absorption and thoroughly clean it for effective detox potential; with third-party testing every step of the way.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The zeolite in Pure Body Extra Strength undergoes a proprietary milling process that reduces the size of each of the zeolite &ldquo;cages&rdquo; to the nanometer range.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Many providers simply mechanically pulverize the zeolite cages, which can damage the cages and &ldquo;break&rdquo; the negative charge, rendering those zeolite cages completely ineffective. Our proprietary processing delivers intact zeolite cages, for negatively-charged zeolites optimally sized for absorption.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We then &ldquo;clean&rdquo; the zeolite in a multi-step proprietary process that releases any existing heavy metals and toxins from the zeolite cages, removes them, and replaces those toxins with the exchangeable cations calcium, magnesium, sodium and potassium.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>These cations are then &ldquo;exchanged&rdquo; in the body when heavy metals and toxins are encountered, giving the body a calcium or magnesium ion in exchange for a lead, mercury, cadmium ion or other toxin. Even so, the &ldquo;amount&rdquo; of calcium, potassium, magnesium or sodium received into the body (in exchange for the toxin) is so minute it is not considered a form of supplementation of that mineral.<\\/p>","pl":"<p>Odpowiednio dobieramy zeolit \\u200b\\u200bw celu uzyskania maksymalnej absorpcji i dok\\u0142adnie oczyszczamy, aby uzyska\\u0107 skuteczny potencja\\u0142 detoksykacyjny; z testowaniem przez strony trzecie na ka\\u017cdym etapie.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Zeolit \\u200b\\u200bw Pure Body Extra Strength podlega zastrze\\u017conemu procesowi mielenia, kt&oacute;ry zmniejsza rozmiar ka\\u017cdej z \\"klatek\\" zeolitu do zakresu nanometr&oacute;w.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Wielu dostawc&oacute;w po prostu mechanicznie rozdrabnia klatki zeolitowe, kt&oacute;re mog\\u0105 uszkodzi\\u0107 klatki i \\"z\\u0142ama\\u0107\\" \\u0142adunek ujemny, czyni\\u0105c te klatki zeolitowe ca\\u0142kowicie nieskutecznymi. Nasze opatentowane przetwarzanie dostarcza nienaruszone klatki zeolitowe dla ujemnie na\\u0142adowanych zeolit&oacute;w o optymalnej wielko\\u015bci do absorpcji.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nast\\u0119pnie \\"oczyszczamy\\" zeolit \\u200b\\u200bw wieloetapowym, zastrze\\u017conym procesie, kt&oacute;ry uwalnia wszelkie istniej\\u0105ce metale ci\\u0119\\u017ckie i toksyny z klatek zeolitowych, usuwa je i zast\\u0119puje te toksyny wymienialnymi kationami wapnia, magnezu, sodu i potasu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Kationy te s\\u0105 nast\\u0119pnie \\"wymieniane\\" w ciele, gdy napotykane s\\u0105 metale ci\\u0119\\u017ckie i toksyny, daj\\u0105c cia\\u0142u jon wapnia lub magnezu w zamian za o\\u0142&oacute;w, rt\\u0119\\u0107, jon kadmu lub inn\\u0105 toksyn\\u0119. Mimo to \\"ilo\\u015b\\u0107\\" wapnia, potasu, magnezu lub sodu otrzymywana w organizmie (w zamian za toksyn\\u0119) jest tak ma\\u0142a, \\u017ce \\u200b\\u200bnie jest uwa\\u017cana za form\\u0119 suplementacji tego minera\\u0142u.<\\/p>","jp":"<p>\\u5f53\\u793e\\u306f\\u3001\\u5438\\u53ce\\u52b9\\u7387\\u3092\\u6700\\u5927\\u9650\\u306b\\u3059\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u3001\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306e\\u30b5\\u30a4\\u30ba\\u3092\\u9069\\u5207\\u306b\\u8abf\\u6574\\u3057\\u3001\\u52b9\\u679c\\u7684\\u306a\\u30c7\\u30c8\\u30c3\\u30af\\u30b9\\u52b9\\u679c\\u306e\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u5b8c\\u5168\\u306a\\u308b\\u6d17\\u6d44\\u3092\\u65bd\\u3057\\u3066\\u3044\\u307e\\u3059\\u3002\\u3055\\u3089\\u306b\\u3001\\u3042\\u3089\\u3086\\u308b\\u65b9\\u6cd5\\u3067\\u7b2c\\u4e09\\u8005\\u671f\\u9593\\u306b\\u3088\\u308b\\u30c6\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u3082\\u5b9f\\u65bd\\u6e08\\u307f\\u3067\\u3059\\u3002<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u30d4\\u30e5\\u30a2\\u30dc\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30a8\\u30af\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30e9\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30ec\\u30f3\\u30b9\\u306e\\u30bc\\u30aa\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30c8\\u306f\\u3001&ldquo;\\u30b1\\u30fc\\u30b8&rdquo;\\u306e\\u